Date: 2 Feb 2005
From: R.J. Ferran <rj@ferran.com>

A friend was out on a sport boat fishing for squid the other day. When
cleaning the squid he found numerous large yellow spots and was afraid to
eat the squid. These were 25-pound types caught off San Diego. Don't know
if this is relevant.
--
R.J. Ferran
<rj@ferran.com>
